metadata.name: BEACH BAR
metadata.description:
Being a Greek, the sea is a huge part of our culture. So, the first place that I wanted to go in order to escape the pandemic was a private beach where I could just listen to the waves, enjoy the sun and read a book. 

Which of your senses are triggered when you think of the beach? Is it the smell of sunscreen everywhere, the warmth of the sun on your skin, the sound of the waves? For me it's all of the above.

Dimensions: 3508 x 3508 px at 300 DPI
File Format: PNG
